1
00:00:27,400 --> 00:00:29,719
=Soft-Hearted God=

2
00:00:29,720 --> 00:00:31,924
=Episode 13=
(Your cuteness)

3
00:00:31,925 --> 00:00:34,157
(became the warmth I crave most.)

4
00:00:41,300 --> 00:00:42,740
(How bold of you, Ye Zhao.)

5
00:00:42,780 --> 00:00:45,780
(Have you fallen for this demon?)

6
00:00:45,860 --> 00:00:47,500
(This divine heart was granted by you.)

7
00:00:47,860 --> 00:00:49,260
(Why would it fall for mortals?)

8
00:00:59,580 --> 00:01:01,900
What's with the thunder all of a sudden?

9
00:01:02,580 --> 00:01:04,900
Boss, let's go home.

10
00:01:11,940 --> 00:01:13,020
Zhao,

11
00:01:13,700 --> 00:01:16,620
your heart is beating fast.

12
00:01:19,140 --> 00:01:20,620
A god's heart

13
00:01:21,060 --> 00:01:22,820
beats faster than a mortal's.

14
00:01:24,660 --> 00:01:26,500
Can we eat now?

15
00:01:27,260 --> 00:01:29,220
No, Her Lady isn't back yet.

16
00:01:29,340 --> 00:01:31,460
Zhao, put me down.

17
00:01:32,940 --> 00:01:34,140
Let's wait a bit longer.

18
00:01:37,420 --> 00:01:39,380
Is your leg better?

19
00:01:40,700 --> 00:01:42,059
I'm just being lazy,

20
00:01:42,060 --> 00:01:43,900
wanting to walk less.

21
00:01:50,780 --> 00:01:51,900
My lady,

22
00:01:52,500 --> 00:01:53,939
you're finally back.

23
00:01:53,940 --> 00:01:55,499
I've reheated the food several times.

24
00:01:55,500 --> 00:01:56,660
Come.

25
00:01:56,700 --> 00:01:57,820
Coming.

26
00:01:58,300 --> 00:01:59,740
Sorry to keep you waiting.

27
00:01:59,860 --> 00:02:02,939
My lady, don't listen to him.

28
00:02:02,940 --> 00:02:05,139
Bai was reading storybooks again.

29
00:02:05,140 --> 00:02:07,740
He didn't practice medicine
or prep herbs.

30
00:02:08,860 --> 00:02:10,419
Don't talk nonsense.

31
00:02:10,420 --> 00:02:12,299
You were the one reading

32
00:02:12,300 --> 00:02:13,579
and crying your eyes out.

33
00:02:13,580 --> 00:02:16,460
I was the one
busy cooking all these dishes.

34
00:02:18,340 --> 00:02:19,939
You're the one crying.

35
00:02:19,940 --> 00:02:21,059
I never cry,

36
00:02:21,060 --> 00:02:22,740
same as you, My lady.

37
00:02:23,980 --> 00:02:26,339
"Oh, the god in the story
has a tragic life."

38
00:02:26,340 --> 00:02:27,779
"He gives up everything for love,"

39
00:02:27,780 --> 00:02:30,100
"only to be killed by the one he loves."

40
00:02:30,500 --> 00:02:31,940
That was you, wasn't it?

41
00:02:32,940 --> 00:02:34,540
You!

42
00:02:34,580 --> 00:02:36,180
Stop right there!

43
00:02:36,220 --> 00:02:37,699
I won't spare you today!

44
00:02:37,700 --> 00:02:38,499
You two.

45
00:02:38,500 --> 00:02:39,059
I didn't!

46
00:02:39,060 --> 00:02:39,859
My lady, look at her.

47
00:02:39,860 --> 00:02:40,939
He's framing me!

48
00:02:40,940 --> 00:02:42,620
(From the moment I gained memory,)

49
00:02:42,860 --> 00:02:44,300
(I've always been alone.)

50
00:02:45,380 --> 00:02:47,495
(Compared to silent meditation,)

51
00:02:48,180 --> 00:02:49,780
(this place feels warm.)

52
00:02:53,180 --> 00:02:54,220
Zhao.

53
00:02:55,180 --> 00:02:55,979
Stop running!

54
00:02:55,980 --> 00:02:57,620
Come eat.

55
00:03:03,260 --> 00:03:04,220
Coming.

56
00:03:08,900 --> 00:03:10,139
Stop!

57
00:03:10,140 --> 00:03:11,900
You two, sit down.

58
00:03:22,900 --> 00:03:23,900
Zhao,

59
00:03:23,980 --> 00:03:25,299
come to my room after dinner.

60
00:03:25,300 --> 00:03:26,500
I need to talk to you.

61
00:03:31,820 --> 00:03:33,980
I'm done eating.

62
00:03:36,580 --> 00:03:37,620
Hurry up.

63
00:03:37,660 --> 00:03:38,740
My lady.

64
00:03:48,380 --> 00:03:50,140
That's my bowl.

65
00:04:04,900 --> 00:04:06,060
Senior.

66
00:04:06,087 --> 00:04:08,482
(Qingxin Pavilion)

67
00:04:18,700 --> 00:04:21,220
Cover your eyes and take off your shirt.

68
00:04:21,260 --> 00:04:22,980
Then stand still and don't move.

69
00:04:23,180 --> 00:04:24,859
Why?

70
00:04:24,860 --> 00:04:26,620
Just do it.

71
00:04:40,740 --> 00:04:42,579
Don't open your eyes

72
00:04:42,580 --> 00:04:44,020
until I say so.

73
00:04:44,860 --> 00:04:46,180
Hurry and take it off.

74
00:04:53,420 --> 00:04:54,620
Don't move.

75
00:05:33,740 --> 00:05:34,740
Boss.

76
00:05:36,462 --> 00:05:37,582
I...

77
00:05:39,420 --> 00:05:41,380
I'm taking your measurements.

78
00:05:41,540 --> 00:05:43,859
You're now part of our hall,

79
00:05:43,860 --> 00:05:46,380
so we need to make you a uniform.

80
00:05:51,540 --> 00:05:53,140
Look at you.

81
00:05:53,980 --> 00:05:55,739
What's wrong with your body?

82
00:05:55,740 --> 00:05:57,380
You're burning hot.

83
00:05:57,820 --> 00:06:00,819
Did you catch a cold?

84
00:06:00,820 --> 00:06:01,940
A divine body

85
00:06:02,420 --> 00:06:05,700
runs hotter than mortals.

86
00:06:06,740 --> 00:06:08,180
Can I open my eyes now?

87
00:06:09,940 --> 00:06:11,060
Go ahead.

88
00:06:18,180 --> 00:06:19,300
Boss,

89
00:06:19,860 --> 00:06:21,260
if you're measuring,

90
00:06:21,300 --> 00:06:22,539
why blindfold me?

91
00:06:22,540 --> 00:06:24,500
We don't have proper tools.

92
00:06:24,660 --> 00:06:26,500
If you look,

93
00:06:27,060 --> 00:06:28,860
I can't do it.

94
00:06:30,620 --> 00:06:32,980
Can I get dressed now?

95
00:06:34,620 --> 00:06:35,700
What?

96
00:06:37,540 --> 00:06:41,060
Even gods feel cold?

97
00:06:51,820 --> 00:06:52,860
Then

98
00:06:53,660 --> 00:06:54,980
I'll take my leave.

99
00:07:03,180 --> 00:07:07,540
Will you guard the door tonight?

100
00:07:15,820 --> 00:07:16,740
(Yes.)

101
00:07:27,540 --> 00:07:29,059
No, I won't wear it!

102
00:07:29,060 --> 00:07:30,499
Zhao, wear it.

103
00:07:30,500 --> 00:07:31,500
It's too feminine.

104
00:07:31,740 --> 00:07:32,419
I won't wear it.

105
00:07:32,420 --> 00:07:33,500
Just wear it.

106
00:07:33,620 --> 00:07:34,739
I won't.

107
00:07:34,740 --> 00:07:36,299
Wear it!

108
00:07:36,300 --> 00:07:36,939
Zhao.

109
00:07:36,940 --> 00:07:37,820
Don't come closer.

110
00:07:41,060 --> 00:07:42,260
I'll help you.

111
00:08:13,060 --> 00:08:14,179
Does he love me?

112
00:08:14,180 --> 00:08:15,619
Or not?

113
00:08:15,620 --> 00:08:16,819
Love me?

114
00:08:16,820 --> 00:08:18,500
Or not?

115
00:08:19,300 --> 00:08:20,380
Love me?

116
00:08:23,300 --> 00:08:24,940
That annoying Ye Zhao!

117
00:08:25,420 --> 00:08:27,500
Am I really that hard to love?

118
00:08:29,620 --> 00:08:30,860
I don't believe it.

119
00:08:31,180 --> 00:08:32,539
You may cry,

120
00:08:32,540 --> 00:08:33,619
you may run,

121
00:08:33,620 --> 00:08:35,860
but you must never give up.

122
00:08:35,980 --> 00:08:37,860
You can do it, Xi.

123
00:08:38,980 --> 00:08:40,099
He doesn't love me.

124
00:08:40,100 --> 00:08:41,539
He loves me.

125
00:08:41,540 --> 00:08:43,180
He doesn't love me.

126
00:08:45,820 --> 00:08:47,300
This is the one.

127
00:08:56,300 --> 00:08:57,300
Come in.

128
00:09:01,180 --> 00:09:03,300
Boss, you called me?

129
00:09:04,860 --> 00:09:07,659
Take these herbs I've picked
and bring them out.

130
00:09:07,660 --> 00:09:08,579
Dry them tomorrow.

131
00:09:08,580 --> 00:09:09,580
Alright.

132
00:09:15,180 --> 00:09:16,620
Anything else?

133
00:09:17,020 --> 00:09:18,059
I'm going to rest.

134
00:09:18,060 --> 00:09:19,179
You may leave.

135
00:09:19,180 --> 00:09:20,260
Yes.

136
00:09:37,700 --> 00:09:39,339
(Interesting.)

137
00:09:39,340 --> 00:09:41,660
You're interesting.

138
00:09:41,940 --> 00:09:44,140
Even my demon heart

139
00:09:44,300 --> 00:09:46,699
has begun to feel love.

140
00:09:46,700 --> 00:09:48,140
I was just about to see you.

141
00:09:49,300 --> 00:09:51,259
I have a solution that benefits us both.

142
00:09:51,260 --> 00:09:53,459
As long as you don't use my body
to do evil,

143
00:09:53,460 --> 00:09:55,380
Zhao won't harm you.

144
00:09:55,540 --> 00:09:57,819
You can live peacefully

145
00:09:57,820 --> 00:09:58,899
inside me.

146
00:09:58,900 --> 00:10:00,500
= Isn't that good?
- No.

147
00:10:01,180 --> 00:10:02,899
Your so-called love

148
00:10:02,900 --> 00:10:04,819
is just for reproduction,

149
00:10:04,820 --> 00:10:06,539
no different from animals.

150
00:10:06,540 --> 00:10:08,819
When someone stronger appears,

151
00:10:08,820 --> 00:10:11,380
love collapses instantly.

152
00:10:13,660 --> 00:10:14,819
You've never loved,

153
00:10:14,820 --> 00:10:17,179
so you have no right to judge mine.

154
00:10:17,180 --> 00:10:18,299
I warn you.

155
00:10:18,300 --> 00:10:20,299
You'd better behave yourself in my body.

156
00:10:20,300 --> 00:10:22,659
If you try to harm Zhao,

157
00:10:22,660 --> 00:10:24,460
I'll die with you.

158
00:10:27,540 --> 00:10:29,860
I basically don't have to do anything.

159
00:10:30,020 --> 00:10:31,939
If a demon and a god unite,

160
00:10:31,940 --> 00:10:33,699
Heaven won't allow it.

161
00:10:33,700 --> 00:10:36,980
Then your so-called love

162
00:10:37,180 --> 00:10:40,020
will be nothing but an illusion.

163
00:10:40,660 --> 00:10:42,260
An illusion.

164
00:10:46,180 --> 00:10:47,260
Zhao!

165
00:10:52,540 --> 00:10:53,620
Zhao!

166
00:10:54,940 --> 00:10:56,100
Zhao!

167
00:10:56,820 --> 00:10:59,020
Hua, Bai!

168
00:11:00,660 --> 00:11:01,980
Where are you all?

169
00:11:03,940 --> 00:11:07,220
They say you're a stray raised
by the whole village.

170
00:11:07,540 --> 00:11:08,780
Let's have a deal.

171
00:11:08,900 --> 00:11:11,340
I'll give you this bone for your bell.

172
00:11:13,700 --> 00:11:14,939
I'll count to three.

173
00:11:14,940 --> 00:11:16,059
If you don't bark,

174
00:11:16,060 --> 00:11:17,539
I'll take it as a yes.

175
00:11:17,540 --> 00:11:18,299
One,

176
00:11:18,300 --> 00:11:19,380
two, three.

177
00:11:20,820 --> 00:11:23,580
You're truly a good friend.

178
00:11:32,325 --> 00:11:34,195
(Baihua Hall)

179
00:11:34,420 --> 00:11:35,500
Hua!

180
00:11:35,820 --> 00:11:36,699
Bai!

181
00:11:36,700 --> 00:11:37,860
Zhao!

182
00:11:39,060 --> 00:11:40,820
Hua! Zhao!

183
00:11:47,287 --> 00:11:48,996
♪Too bad the rain will stop♪

184
00:11:48,997 --> 00:11:51,846
♪The wind will fade,
tomorrow will clear♪

185
00:11:51,847 --> 00:11:54,586
♪I'd rather this night never end♪

186
00:11:54,587 --> 00:11:56,216
♪Let the long shadows♪

187
00:11:56,217 --> 00:12:01,817
♪whisper what's in your heart♪

188
00:12:01,867 --> 00:12:03,466
♪If in a dream♪

189
00:12:03,467 --> 00:12:06,226
♪I can hear your voice♪

190
00:12:06,227 --> 00:12:09,076
♪Then let it be our meeting♪

191
00:12:09,077 --> 00:12:11,676
♪Let it be us♪

192
00:12:11,677 --> 00:12:16,466
♪drawing endlessly close♪

193
00:12:16,467 --> 00:12:18,226
♪Too bad the rain will stop♪

194
00:12:18,227 --> 00:12:20,877
♪The wind will fade,
tomorrow will clear♪

195
00:12:21,097 --> 00:12:23,816
♪I can't even hold you properly♪

196
00:12:23,817 --> 00:12:25,466
♪Not even in time♪

197
00:12:25,467 --> 00:12:31,126
♪to tell you how I feel♪

198
00:12:31,127 --> 00:12:32,666
♪If the rain won't stop♪

199
00:12:32,667 --> 00:12:35,416
♪If the wind won't fade,
if time stands still♪

200
00:12:35,417 --> 00:12:38,386
♪Let love go on♪

201
00:12:38,387 --> 00:12:40,936
♪Until forever♪

202
00:12:40,937 --> 00:12:45,576
♪Until we slowly grow old♪

203
00:12:45,577 --> 00:12:48,186
♪Until forever♪

204
00:12:48,187 --> 00:12:55,297
♪Until we slowly grow old♪
